Subject: Connectivity problem agent-server custom port
Description: Estimated, We need to resolve connectivity problem from agent-server on custom port. We have ping to server but appliance is not responding at defined custom port. We could meet on: 12/03 10:30 a 12:00 hs 13/03 15:00 a 18:00 hs 14/03 10:00 a 14:00 hs Participants are: mamigo@aconseg.com afleming@TPSV.CL esquadrito@TPSV.CL larratia@TPSV.CL
Solution_Comment__c:
We removed the Custom Client Certificate set on the UI, changed the port to 443 on the client and after that both EPP clients connected to the EPP server.

We have also uploaded the SSL certificate on the EPP server and after that it was secure.
